DaynaPORT SCSI/Link Linux driver -- change history

0.2  2026-06-09
     - RX: batch up to 2 frames per READ(6) (SCSILINK_RX_REQ 1524 -> 4096),
       ~75% speed increase.

0.1  2026-06-09
     Initial release.
     - Builds as a loadable module against any configured Linux 2.0.x kernel
     Driver tested on i386 / Adaptec AHA-1542 / BlueSCSI V2.
